An elegant dish. Would make an elegant buffet dish. My first time making duck! Served it for Christmas. Be sure you carefully trim all the excess duck fat so you get a nice crisp skin on your bird. I froze the duck fat, thinking that I'll render it and try a Basque dish that calls for duck fat!

